00:57:03.100 --> 00:57:06.660
Pazite se.

00:58:13.180 --> 00:58:15.260
Molim te, molim te.

00:58:42.220 --> 00:58:45.820
Hajde!

00:58:50.660 --> 00:58:52.500
Stani, stani!
